name: Contemplation
description:
In a reality far removed from our civilization-damaged perception, a lifestyle is contemplated as what we call god. This species, stripped of any limiting rules, contemplates its pisic mushroom gardens. Its logic of community is given by perception and the search for truth, art being its only task, the activity of all species on this planet is radically individualistic,
By @glauberbnunes
